{"tid":2365894,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【撞衫不可怕系列】IU VS 崔素拉：一個嫵媚一個帥氣","createTime":"2021-01-14T05:57:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T17:13:08.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"668911d2e63566fe2311a5d77534b7b29916850a","tid":2365894,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T05:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_aa2e58c04fece50d1a99d714abaef255/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-13/132971-893118.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_aa2e58c04fece50d1a99d714abaef255%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-13%2F132971-893118.png&h=c251cb95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n甜心IU撞衫超模崔素拉，誰更勝一籌呢？<br />\n<br />\n娛樂圈撞衫是常有的事情，這次IU就撞衫了超模崔素拉。 日前IU出席了第35屆Golden Disc Awards（金唱片大賞），深色西裝外套搭配白襯衣，下衣失蹤的造型配上一雙黑色緊身過膝高跟皮靴，立顯大長腿。 一頭溫柔的長髮中和了西裝和皮靴的帥氣，多了一些嫵媚和甜美。 又甜又酷的造型為IU加分不少。 作為G奢侈品牌大使的IU還戴上了G牌的項鏈和胸針，小配飾讓整體造型更加精緻。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_4d85023d13dcc0479d692e5d60599fdb/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-13/132971-893115.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_4d85023d13dcc0479d692e5d60599fdb%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-13%2F132971-893115.png&h=0b89c42c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU的這套服裝是韓國Y品牌，品牌的新片宣傳冊上，韓國知名超模崔素拉也穿上IU的同款服裝，只是將過膝皮靴換成了綁帶尖頭高跟鞋，將下衣失蹤演繹到了極致，崔素拉的修長筆直的美腿讓女生們看了直喊羨慕。 不同於IU的溫柔長髮，崔素拉梳著幹練的髮型，配上一對圓形大耳環，用紅唇點綴，像極了韓劇裡的職場女精英。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ec35527d482f9f67bf27241e92d7531d/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-13/132971-893117.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_ec35527d482f9f67bf27241e92d7531d%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-13%2F132971-893117.png&h=13fbfacf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ee75e889a37bca57e6df87f3812ab84758b61f7","tid":2365894,"uid":60286,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:03:20.000Z","msg":"唔識欣賞超模<br />\n成個男人咁"},{"pid":"f3c2ee9d770492af0ef2a8b98ca352fc0abd3057","tid":2365894,"uid":30510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ee75e889a37bca57e6df87f3812ab84758b61f7","tid":2365894,"uid":60286,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:03:20.000Z","msg":"唔識欣賞超模<br />\n成個男人咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:04:25.000Z","msg":"我老母都靚過佢"},{"pid":"04152b2644a4b2ddfd9881204ebda0b8e6818be5","tid":2365894,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:08:38.000Z","msg":"一個係女人 一個.....唔識講"},{"pid":"9f04f83cfa67fe659efcc031709c97b5c32b9e62","tid":2365894,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T17:13:08.000Z","msg":"女 vs 男<br />\n唔公平"}]}